README for slitaz-mercurial-style
================================================================================

This is the template for our so famous and so used Hg repositories.

Install: /usr/lib/python2.7/site-packages/mercurial/templates/slitaz

To work on it you need hgweb.cgi (with it's config file), Lighttpd with CGI Python
support.

To use it locally you can install the package: slitaz-mercurial-style and use 
a config file that looks like below or use a single repo with a modified .hgrc
configuration file.

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# hgweb.config - Hg web interface configuration
#

[collections]
/home/pankso/Projects = /home/pankso/Projects

[web]
style = slitaz
allow_archive = gz bz2
baseurl = /

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
